zh: 嘿，雜魚！今天又來送人頭嗎？
en: Hey, trash fish! Are you here for feeding again today?

zh: 我才不是雜魚呢！我只是還在學習
en: I'm not a trash fish! I'm just still learning

zh: 學習？你確定不是在進行「菜」的高級研究嗎？看來你已經取得了博士學位
en: Study? Are you sure you're not conducting advanced research on "dishes"? It seems you already have a Ph.D.

zh: 雜魚~這麽快就扛不住了
該死的小鬼，欺人太甚，不知道我的病毒有沒成功注入
en: Damn the kid. It is really push it too far. I don't know if my virus was successfully injected.
Turn on the computer and take a look

zh: 看到由程序生成了捷徑。打開試試能不能駭進她的電腦
en: See shortcuts generated by the program. Open it and see if you can hack into her computer.

zh: 駭進去了(WSAD鍵 / 方向鍵移動)
en: Hack went in ( WSAD keys / arrow keys movement )

zh: 可惡，還有一層防火墙保護
en: Damn, there is firewall protection here

zh: 咦，右邊有個Bug，可以利用這Bug破解這層的防火墙
en: Hey, there is a bug on the right. You can use this bug to crack this layer of firewall
